Specifications:
Home
Desk Calendars
Wall Calendars: Perfect for hanging in homes, offices, and workspaces.
Desk Calendars: Compact and ideal for desks or workstations, these calendars are often designed to stand upright.
Framed Calendars: These high-quality desk calendars have a professional and sleek design, ideal for those who want a decorative touch along with the functionality of a calendar.
Wall Calendars: Available in A3.
Desk Calendars: Standard sizes include A5, 10 x 3.5 in, 4.7 x 5.7 in, and 8 x 8 in.
Framed Calendars: Available in sizes such as 4.7 x 5.7 in, 9.25 x 9.25 in, 9.25 x 6.75 in
Wall Calendar: Ideal for hanging on a wall. These calendars often come with a larger size and multiple pages.
Desk Calendar: A compact, stand-up design, perfect for keeping on your desk or workspace. Typically smaller and can be single-page or flip-style.
Framed Calendar: A more elegant option with a frame, often printed on premium paper, and ready to hang. These calendars offer a more decorative appeal in addition to functionality.
Add your own photos, artwork, or logos to the calendar pages.
Choose the layout, design, and even the size of your calendar.
Upload your own file with special dates, such as birthdays or anniversaries, to make the calendar more personal.

Specifications:
Home
Case Bound Diaries
Add company logos, taglines, and custom designs.
Order in bulk at discounted rates.
Personalize individual diaries with names, roles, or specific messages for employees or clients.
Premium Look & Feel: Case bound diaries have a high-end, elegant appeal, making them perfect for business or professional use.
Durability: The hardcover provides protection and helps the diary maintain its shape even after frequent use.
Formal Appearance: Ideal for meetings, presentations, or as a gift for clients or employees.
Volume Discounts for large orders.
Personalized Options for each diary in the bulk order (such as custom names or logos).
Delivery to multiple locations for corporate or event-related needs.
Choose a Case Bound Diary if you need a durable, formal, and sophisticated diary for professional use.
Choose a Wiro Diary if you need a flexible, portable, and practical diary for everyday use, or if you prefer a diary that can lie flat for easier writing.
Case Bound Diaries: Typically available in 216 x 145 mm. Custom sizes can also be offered upon request for bulk orders
Wiro Diaries: Common sizes include A5, and B5. Since they are wire-bound, the pages tend to be slightly more flexible than case-bound options.
Leatherette Covers: For a classy and sophisticated look.
Fabric Covers: Offering a soft, textured finish.
Paper Covers: Available for those seeking a more eco-friendly or minimalist option.
Flexibility: Wiro diaries can be opened 360°, making it easier to write in all corners of the page.
Compact & Portable: Wiro diaries are generally more lightweight and flexible, ideal for on-the-go use.
Lays Flat: They are easy to use for people who need to take quick notes, sketches, or ideas, as they can lay flat without the book closing on its own.
